    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">打造你的装备。碾压虫潮。在废墟之城中生存。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数十年前，一场灾难性事件几乎将人类从世界上抹去。变异虫群从废墟中崛起，占领整座城市，将高楼化为巢穴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一名雇佣兵，是少数敢于突破虫群封锁、深入沦陷城区的幸存者之一。你的任务是带回所有人都不敢触碰的战利品：虫族残骸。它们价值高昂、性质不稳定，却是新世界中最重要的资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880100/extras/b17251b428421b0d9254979f9648814a.avif?t=1772043050\" width=1170 height=708 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">⚔️ 快节奏高强度波次战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冲刺、射击、爆破、斩杀，在不断进化的虫潮中杀出重围。战斗中获取武器，强化合成，构筑属于你的强力流派，只为撑到撤离的那一刻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自动射击与手动瞄准结合的战斗系统<br>单局节奏紧凑，爽快刺激，可无限重玩<br>数百种道具，近乎无限的流派组合</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880100/extras/618e85088e3510fe8af4971d23d2a671.poster.avif?t=1772043050\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880100/extras/618e85088e3510fe8af4971d23d2a671.webm?t=1772043050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880100/extras/618e85088e3510fe8af4971d23d2a671.mp4?t=1772043050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">🎒 背包决定你的构筑强度</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的背包是你的流派核心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有武器、饰品、配件与特殊物品都必须放入网格背包中。摆放位置、相邻关系与朝向都会影响效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特形状与机制的道具设计<br>通过排列组合触发强力联动<br>合成升级，打造更强装备</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合理规划空间，活得更久。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880100/extras/0f2086f84d4d4af8f741df476b6bb6c4.poster.avif?t=1772043050\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880100/extras/0f2086f84d4d4af8f741df476b6bb6c4.webm?t=1772043050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880100/extras/0f2086f84d4d4af8f741df476b6bb6c4.mp4?t=1772043050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">🏗️ 建设战略前哨基地，获得永久成长</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >突袭城市，获取资源。在每一局之间扩建你的前哨基地，解锁永久强化与更多可能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造工坊、军械库、贸易站等设施<br>解锁新的雇佣兵与开局配置<br>提升难度，挑战更高风险，赢取更丰厚奖励</p>",
